edu.lehigh.cse.lol

Class Config

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.lehigh.cse.lol.Config

  • public class Config
extends java.lang.Object
    Config stores game-specific configuration values.

    A programmer should extend Config, and change these values in their class constructor.
